sp.p:
              
              No, you are too young, and I am much too old; 

              Aye and unworthy, and the world will say,

              We married not for love, good morrow servant.

              
              
                So at the first, she kissed very strangely, close, and untoward; 

                then said I to her, think but upon the wrongs, the

                intolerable wrong, the rogue your Husband does you.
